{"tid":2411424,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣海巡艦艇在蔡英文指示下新增TAIWAN字樣","createTime":"2021-02-17T10:16:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:16:24.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"412dd96ef005912784ca9ba43f39fa232065221d","tid":2411424,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:16:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576025-20210217.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576025-20210217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN26hYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=4a5edc4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576025-20210217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=afa1a436\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576025-20210217.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n在台灣，總統府表示，海巡艦艇新增台灣的英文字樣TAIWAN，正是蔡英文總統的指示。發言人說，面對灰色地帶衝突的應對，加上TAIWAN字樣，能讓海巡艦艇有更清楚的辨識、更安全的執法。<br />\n<br />\n總統府發言人張惇涵在社交網站發文表示，在守衛海疆的任務上，海巡甚至比海軍更前線，除了巡防任務外，也要執行海上救援救難，以及查緝走私、打擊犯罪等治安工作。海巡夥伴時常需要在第一線、近距離執法，去年底馬祖海域大量違法抽砂船事件，就是海巡艦艇負責執法驅離。"}]}